{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"First of all, I'm a geek."},{"time":4000,"text":"I'm an organic food-eating,"},{"time":6000,"text":"carbon footprint-minimizing, robotic surgery geek."},{"time":9000,"text":"And I really want to build green,"},{"time":12000,"text":"but I'm very suspicious"},{"time":14000,"text":"of all of these well-meaning articles,"},{"time":16000,"text":"people long on moral authority"},{"time":18000,"text":"and short on data,"},{"time":20000,"text":"telling me how to do these kinds of things."},{"time":22000,"text":"And so I have to figure this out for myself."},{"time":24000,"text":"For example: Is this evil?"},{"time":27000,"text":"I have dropped a blob of organic yogurt"},{"time":30000,"text":"from happy self-actualized local cows"},{"time":32000,"text":"on my counter top,"},{"time":34000,"text":"and I grab a paper towel and I want to wipe it up."},{"time":37000,"text":"But can I use a paper towel? (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"The answer to this can be found in embodied energy."},{"time":43000,"text":"This is the amount of energy that goes into"},{"time":45000,"text":"any paper towel or embodied water,"},{"time":47000,"text":"and every time I use a paper towel,"},{"time":49000,"text":"I am using this much"},{"time":51000,"text":"virtual energy and water."},{"time":53000,"text":"Wipe it up, throw it away."},{"time":55000,"text":"Now, if I compare that to a cotton towel"},{"time":58000,"text":"that I can use a thousand times,"},{"time":60000,"text":"I don't have a whole lot of embodied energy"},{"time":63000,"text":"until I wash that yogurty towel."},{"time":65000,"text":"This is now operating energy."},{"time":68000,"text":"So if I throw my towel in the washing machine,"},{"time":70000,"text":"I've now put energy and water"},{"time":72000,"text":"back into that towel ..."},{"time":74000,"text":"unless I use a front-loading, high-efficiency washing machine, (Laughter)"},{"time":76000,"text":"and then it looks a little bit better."},{"time":79000,"text":"But what about a recycled paper towel"},{"time":81000,"text":"that comes in those little half sheets?"},{"time":83000,"text":"Well, now a paper towel looks better."},{"time":85000,"text":"Screw the paper towels. Let's go to a sponge."},{"time":87000,"text":"I wipe it up with a sponge, and I put it under the running water,"},{"time":90000,"text":"and I have a lot less energy and a lot more water."},{"time":92000,"text":"Unless you're like me and you leave the handle"},{"time":94000,"text":"in the position of hot even when you turn it on,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and then you start to use more energy."},{"time":98000,"text":"Or worse, you let it run until it's warm"},{"time":100000,"text":"to rinse out your towel."},{"time":102000,"text":"And now all bets are off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"So what this says is that"},{"time":108000,"text":"sometimes the things that you least expect --"},{"time":111000,"text":"the position in which you put the handle --"},{"time":113000,"text":"have a bigger effect than any of those other things"},{"time":115000,"text":"that you were trying to optimize."},{"time":117000,"text":"Now imagine someone as twisted as me"},{"time":119000,"text":"trying to build a house."},{"time":121000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":124000,"text":"That's what my husband and I are doing right now."},{"time":127000,"text":"And so, we wanted to know, how green could we be?"},{"time":129000,"text":"And there's a thousand and one articles out there"},{"time":131000,"text":"telling us how to make all these green trade-offs."},{"time":133000,"text":"And they are just as suspect"},{"time":135000,"text":"in telling us to optimize these little things around the edges"},{"time":138000,"text":"and missing the elephant in the living room."},{"time":140000,"text":"Now, the average house"},{"time":142000,"text":"has about 300 megawatt hours"},{"time":145000,"text":"of embodied energy in it;"},{"time":147000,"text":"this is the energy it takes to make it --"},{"time":149000,"text":"millions and millions of paper towels."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151000,"text":"We wanted to know how much better we could do."},{"time":154000,"text":"And so, like many people,"},{"time":156000,"text":"we start with a house on a lot,"},{"time":158000,"text":"and I'm going to show you a typical construction on the top"},{"time":160000,"text":"and what we're doing on the bottom."},{"time":162000,"text":"So first, we demolish it."},{"time":164000,"text":"It takes some energy, but if you deconstruct it --"},{"time":167000,"text":"you take it all apart, you use the bits --"},{"time":169000,"text":"you can get some of that energy back."},{"time":171000,"text":"We then dug a big hole"},{"time":173000,"text":"to put in a rainwater catchment tank"},{"time":175000,"text":"to take our yard water independent."},{"time":177000,"text":"And then we poured a big foundation"},{"time":179000,"text":"for passive solar."},{"time":181000,"text":"Now, you can reduce the embodied energy"},{"time":183000,"text":"by about 25 percent"},{"time":185000,"text":"by using high fly ash concrete."},{"time":188000,"text":"We then put in framing."},{"time":190000,"text":"And so this is framing -- lumber,"},{"time":192000,"text":"composite materials --"},{"time":194000,"text":"and it's kind of hard to get the embodied energy out of that,"},{"time":197000,"text":"but it can be a sustainable resource"},{"time":199000,"text":"if you use FSC-certified lumber."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"We then go on to"},{"time":204000,"text":"the first thing that was very surprising."},{"time":206000,"text":"If we put aluminum windows in this house,"},{"time":209000,"text":"we would double the energy use right there."},{"time":212000,"text":"Now, PVC is a little bit better,"},{"time":214000,"text":"but still not as good as the wood that we chose."},{"time":217000,"text":"We then put in plumbing,"},{"time":219000,"text":"electrical and HVAC,"},{"time":221000,"text":"and insulate."},{"time":223000,"text":"Now, spray foam is an excellent insulator -- it fills in all the cracks --"},{"time":226000,"text":"but it is pretty high embodied energy,"},{"time":229000,"text":"and, sprayed-in cellulose or blue jeans"},{"time":232000,"text":"is a much lower energy alternative to that."},{"time":234000,"text":"We also used straw bale"},{"time":236000,"text":"infill for our library,"},{"time":238000,"text":"which has zero embodied energy."},{"time":240000,"text":"When it comes time to sheetrock,"},{"time":242000,"text":"if you use EcoRock it's about a quarter"},{"time":244000,"text":"of the embodied energy of standard sheetrock."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247000,"text":"And then you get to the finishes,"},{"time":249000,"text":"the subject of all of those \"go green\" articles,"},{"time":252000,"text":"and on the scale of a house"},{"time":253000,"text":"they almost make no difference at all."},{"time":256000,"text":"And yet, all the press is focused on that."},{"time":258000,"text":"Except for flooring."},{"time":260000,"text":"If you put carpeting in your house,"},{"time":262000,"text":"it's about a tenth of the embodied energy of the entire house,"},{"time":265000,"text":"unless you use concrete or wood"},{"time":267000,"text":"for a much lower embodied energy."},{"time":269000,"text":"So now we add in the final construction energy, we add it all up,"},{"time":272000,"text":"and we've built a house for less than half"},{"time":274000,"text":"of the typical embodied energy for building a house like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"But before we pat ourselves"},{"time":279000,"text":"too much on the back,"},{"time":281000,"text":"we have poured 151 megawatt hours"},{"time":284000,"text":"of energy into constructing this house"},{"time":286000,"text":"when there was a house there before."},{"time":288000,"text":"And so the question is:"},{"time":290000,"text":"How could we make that back?"},{"time":292000,"text":"And so if I run my new energy-efficient house forward,"},{"time":295000,"text":"compared with the old, non-energy-efficient house,"},{"time":298000,"text":"we make it back in about six years."},{"time":301000,"text":"Now, I probably would have upgraded the old house"},{"time":303000,"text":"to be more energy-efficient,"},{"time":305000,"text":"and in that case,"},{"time":307000,"text":"it would take me more about 20 years to break even."},{"time":311000,"text":"Now, if I hadn't paid attention to embodied energy,"},{"time":313000,"text":"it would have taken us"},{"time":315000,"text":"over 50 years to break even"},{"time":317000,"text":"compared to the upgraded house."},{"time":319000,"text":"So what does this mean?"},{"time":321000,"text":"On the scale of my portion of the house,"},{"time":324000,"text":"this is equivalent to about"},{"time":326000,"text":"as much as I drive in a year,"},{"time":328000,"text":"it's about five times as much"},{"time":330000,"text":"as if I went entirely vegetarian."},{"time":332000,"text":"But my elephant in the living room flies."},{"time":335000,"text":"Clearly, I need to walk home from TED."},{"time":338000,"text":"But all the calculations"},{"time":341000,"text":"for embodied energy are on the blog."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"And, remember, it's sometimes the things that you are not expecting"},{"time":346000,"text":"to be the biggest changes that are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349000,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}